<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200907/368b0f97653e4d4487c207813e325554.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200907/910bccd7c97746e692509a0b66584cec.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200907/e3eee4b8377447bcb58b609af02967fb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200907/7a90671aec694b5eafe017275c0ffe4c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200907/f48cbaac61b24d83bc7249360e6372b1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">魔都火锅串串层出不穷，最近人广又曝出一家<strong>「极简风串串店」</strong>，深扒妹第一时间去尝了“鲜”！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200907/6d46257351054a8c8aa6c9f30aa27b72.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">整家店不走传统川渝市井风。简洁大气的蓝白色调，用餐氛围超舒适der~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>· 四川空运来的牛油锅底 ·</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200907/bbc5a953b7fc4feca673f682973c1a3d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>\\\</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200907/5fc14768d7574f71a97ca89befba76d7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">锅底是串串的灵魂，只用从<strong>四川空运来的牛油</strong>。锅底每天现烧，红油翻滚，香辣四溢，真正做到<strong>辣不刺喉</strong>，<strong>麻不泛苦</strong>。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>· 3种鸳鸯锅底 ·</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200907/8e82a99eb48c4fde813a4b42fa99b0a7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这里还有鸳鸯锅可选，<strong>三鲜</strong>、<strong>菌汤</strong>、<strong>番茄</strong>CP红汤底。高汤用牛棒骨、碎牛肉、鸡架骨慢炖20+h，十足的麻辣过瘾和鲜香回味，巴适得板！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200907/ad9ea55bb5ee4b7794857dff771b82ac.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>· 玩出10+种花样的牛肉串 ·</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200907/ad0319e0ae6b43f8aa309bac5750c1f5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这里的牛肉串串放大招了！香菜牛肉、薄荷牛肉、金针菇牛肉…<strong>光牛肉能玩出10+种花样</strong>，堪称“<strong>花心牛肉串串</strong>”！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>· 罕见的清新薄荷串串 ·</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200907/253aad1f916346b9b7078b42f337ebc9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200907/a88bdd5bbee84e61befbcf60034dfba0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-right">△薄荷牛肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">推荐大家试试这款<strong>罕见的薄荷牛肉</strong>！当麻辣爽嫩的小牛肉遇上小清新，不论是谁都能把薄荷牛肉吃个“片甲不留”。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200907/d00da8849c3d4a2980a1fa2b57fc2ba8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200907/b6fbbaeb2c00412581e7ff52755db141.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-right">△缸豆牛肉，△大根牛肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">没想到每款牛肉搭配都能给人惊喜，<strong>每串足足4g</strong>，<strong>性价比up</strong>。在红汤里翻滚，麻辣鲜香的口舌刺激令人上头！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>· 先煮后拌，超入味 ·</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200907/df855ee54d344aed8977567ef07b6e4b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200907/34f2c6378a5741a587b9e4d26ed85111.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">分享一个<strong>暴风吃法</strong>！觉得红汤不过瘾的，可以抄起一把串串，全部<strong>丢在干碟拌着吃</strong>，这样简直入味又上瘾！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>· 80+种品种，1元1串 ·</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200907/c960f40f4cb44d6caccfaaf2b739ff9e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>\\\</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200907/0047fc70dcee4abf9bfa47ba8509fda2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200907/0457a6c4ccb845ccafe64028e97ec2d5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>80+种串串涮菜</strong>，1元1签，全是每天现穿！用极简风的原木调盘子来装盛，分量十足，想吃多少自己拿~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200907/b0120521d73149818f55fc9f1236f2c3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200907/6a4b156bee8d45fcae361fb871ae8e83.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>每天进货的新鲜牛肉</strong>，争分夺秒拼的就是一个“鲜”字！吊龙、嫩牛肉、雪花牛肉...一头牛只有精华肉才有资格上桌~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>· 现切现卖，明档可见 ·</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200907/941e3cd12673441cbfa663bab046cda9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>\\\</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200907/77618260ade9436387dbb4272eac29e9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200907/a7c3c48aea9941ff8d763282f740dca6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店内只供现切现卖的黄牛肉，<strong>明档窗口可见</strong>！看图和摆盘知道师傅的精湛刀工，每一片都肥瘦均匀~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>· 争分夺秒拼新鲜！挂盘牛肉 ·</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200907/6b79833131334ae487a40bd1593d15a8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-right">△吊龙</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店里的<strong>招牌吊龙</strong>，取于肉眼两侧的嫩滑牛肉，连筋带肉。不管怎么转都绝不会掉落，秒杀冰鲜货！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200907/3c361d3c54094d2894a1319cdf3842ce.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在红汤里翻滚后，牛油的香气充斥口腔。大口吃肉的快感，谁吃谁知道！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>· 软糯娇嫩的巴蜀牛肉 ·</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200907/7bcabd70b5654e6e822350a3ce4cde4f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-right">△巴蜀牛肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">鲜嫩多汁的巴蜀牛肉，新鲜到自带黏性挂盘稳稳der。吃起来香滑饱满，略带一丢丢嚼劲~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>· 毛刺分明的新西兰脆毛肚 ·</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200907/b685b46b60ac41d384f612b6e4ff5b49.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200907/d452ad959fd340ccac449808277ce07c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-right">△脆毛肚</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">毛刺根根分明的新西兰脆毛肚，牛油汤底滚一滚，用一下“<strong>7上8下</strong>”火锅秘诀，片片Q弹脆嫩！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>· 还有这些火锅必涮菜 ·</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200907/e2200d09cf86441f96f6eb7e6a15f395.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200907/1e4c71de06f143b1b2e16792684c3537.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-right">△香菜丸子，△现打虾滑</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">纯手工制作的香菜丸子，紧实弹牙；现打虾滑也是分量十足的，鲜辣中带有一丝温柔感，绝了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200907/d28938919eee4f89ac89d720ed25913c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200907/caf7ea9124e542b7bcae0c0dd758478d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">除了吃串串，还能<strong>来几份小吃打打牙祭</strong>！川蜀吃货必点的冒脑花、宽粉、狼牙土豆......<strong>道道都是经典</strong>。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200907/195c7aaedee04bb6a4e75fd64901dce0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200907/2fef11864b0b48609b1e3d7957cebf8f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">金灿灿的小酥肉，酥脆弹牙；糯叽叽的红糖糍粑，绵密Q弹~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>· 来就送！萌爪双皮奶 ·</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200907/9d1bd456a7404bf197ec550cd55c8b27.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">老板超壕气，来就送萌爪双皮奶！QQ弹弹，不限量哦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200907/8bf8f25794ce40ca82aa17f702380859.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200907/67c9f5dd718047ef8a4cd44814e5fdc1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店内坚决不出“老签”，只用一次性签！听到“<strong>折断越多</strong>，<strong>折扣越大</strong>”，深扒妹用尽全身小鸟力气<strong>折断28根</strong>，pick了<strong>8.8折</strong>撸串！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200907/926845bf840b4b9d80ead363eb5383cf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">最后只能默默羡慕隔壁桌的大力士，暴风折断<strong>108根签</strong>，妥妥get<strong>1.8折</strong>撸串！</p>
